Many of the players in the national team are [[Brazil]]ians of Italian descent (Italo-Brazilians). For example, all players of the [[2008 FIFA Futsal World Cup|2008 World Cup]] squad were born in Brazil.<ref>{{cite web|title=Brazil, Spain favorites at Futsal WC|url=http://www.sportsya.com/english/news.php/The_rivalry_between_Brazil_and_Spain_will_be_renewed_in_Futsal_World_Cup.html?id_estruc=283&id=189031|accessdate=2008-12-12}}</ref>
== Honours == === World Achievements === * The Italy national futsal team have appeared in the final match of [[World Futsal Championship]] ([[FIFA Futsal World Cup 2004|2004]])<ref>{{cite web|title=FIFA Futsal World Cup Overview|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesf/futsal-wc.html|publisher=[[RSSSF]]|accessdate=2007-04-12}}</ref>
=== European Achievements === * The Italy national futsal team have won [[UEFA Futsal Championship]] once (2003), came as Runners-up once (2007), and appeared in four third/fourth place playoffs<ref name="Europe" />
